16 deems necessary and proper from time to time;
17 (c) Determine the number of divisions, departments, bureaus, offices, and
18 agencies needed for the successful conduct of the affairs of the university or
19 college; and
20 (d) Grant diplomas and confer degrees upon the recommendation of the president
21 and faculty.
