21 technology center, technology center, technical college, or similar designation; and
22 (25) "Learning outcomes" means the knowledge, skills, and abilities that students have
23 attained as a result of their involvement in a particular set of educational
24 experiences.
25 Section 12. KRS 164.7011 is amended to read as follows:
26 As used in KRS 164.7011 to 164.7021:
27 (1) "Advisory committee" means the Kentucky Aerospace, Aviation, and Defense
